{"tid":2146184,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Carrie 明白嘅 唔好睇FaceBook囉 Quit FaceBook囉主動註銷囉","createTime":"2020-08-08T11:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:00:22.000Z","uid":140538,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a9c3a1a226f65ea5c988a4f57d64016a3dc77a","tid":2146184,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"Carrie<br />\n明白嘅 唔好睇FaceBook囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Quit FaceBook囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主動註銷囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你成日都會見到我㗎btw<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我有好多budget喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw Carrie我比一個建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔鍾意quit左FaceBook佢得唔得o5ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得唔得兩種野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係唔鍾意嘅quit左FaceBook佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我可以guarantee一樣野你會不停見到我嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好問啲咁幼稚嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為當你睇夠5秒就會charge我啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我嗱嗱臨快啲skip咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係點樣你識唔識做生意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解會一個名牌人走出嚟因為多人識呀嘛係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔明白呢個道理我相信你唔係點做生意嘅人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識嘅可以學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得唔得Carrie<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔鍾意FaceBook嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以唔睇Delete咗個app佢好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一個係Uncle TRUMP俾你嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">you don't like it quit it don't complaint唔好喺度</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhMgz8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhMgz8b.jpg&h=5eed853b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑完唔好忘記：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWFQEzU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWFQEzU.jpg&h=7956a98e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTwitter 手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<br />\n以後大家無藉口喇<br />\n快啲bookmark 佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=50e41a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n入bot 拎24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=d36c7ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdwXjAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdwXjAw.jpg&h=cbae2da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我必須提醒各位 下星期有近150名身負暴動罪手足再上庭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/21447450/08/2020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/21447450/08/2020</a> -- 1118油麻地 15名 (1430 西九龍裁判法院) <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%